title: OHL - im westen nichts neues
description:
Rarity, german punkrock from the early 1980ies

OHL - Im Westen nichts neues, 2 CD set, 128 kbps

59 tracks

comment: despite the often provoking lyrics and their band name,
OHL never was a band that sympathised with the neonazi movement
in germany. They were against any kind of political and religious 
systems or movements and more of this, ignorance.

tracks on cd 1 are rather 3 accords tracks of beginners,
while cd 2 contains 3 accord tracks that sound more experienced.
